Instructions for bringing in a new version of half
---------------------------------------------------------------

Current version: ilmbase-2.2.0
Source can be found at: https://github.com/openexr/openexr/tree/master/IlmBase/Half

1. Copy in the new files.
    ```bash
    cp /some/half/half.* .
    ```
2. Apply the patch file. This will add namespaces and use our export macros.
    ```bash
    patch -s -p0 < pxr-half.patch
    ```
    
How to update the patchfile
--------------------------------
If you need to manually make some edits, and thus need to 
generate a new patch file, run the following command.

```bash
diff -ruN -x README 
          -x pxr-half.patch
		  -x halfExport.h
		  -x halfFunction.h
		  -x halfLimits.h
		  -x toFloat.cpp
   		  -x eLut.cpp
		  -x Makefile.am
		  -x Makefile.in
		  -x CMakeLists.txt
          -x README
          half/ 
		  .
> pxr-half.patch
```
